  "body": "introduced by https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15204\r\ncc: @alwx\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Open a chat with a significant number of messages.\r\n2. Scroll to any position within the chat view.\r\n3. Tap on the composer to begin typing a message.\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nAfter tapping on the composer, the chat view automatically scrolls to the bottom, bringing the latest messages into view\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/3ec48d1f-c3a2-499c-ba62-6b089890cb8f\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nTapping on the composer should not trigger an automatic scroll to the bottom of the chat view.\r\n\r\n### Device: \r\n- Real device: Pixel 7a, Android 13\r\n- Android Emulator: Pixel XL API 29",
